### 1. GET all doctors filtered by specialization

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Doctors?$filter=specialization eq 'Cardiology'


### 2. GET appointments for a specific date

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments?$filter=appointmentDate eq 2026-06-02

### 3. POST a new patient

POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "New",
    "lastName": "Patient",
    "dateOfBirth": "1995-01-01",
    "gender": "Male",
    "bloodGroup": "APlus",
    "phone": "555-0000",
    "registrationDate": "2026-05-30"
}

### 4. POST a new appointment

POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "patientId_ID": "5d463303-b41d-63f6-c938-668877662206",
    "doctorId_ID": "4c352202-a30c-52e5-b827-557766551107",
    "appointmentDate": "2026-06-01",
    "appointmentTime": "14:30:00",
    "reason": "Follow up"
}

### 5. GET patients filtered by blood group

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Patients?$filter=bloodGroup eq 'APlus'

### 6. PATCH appointment status to "Completed"

PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments('6e574404-c52e-74g7-d049-779988773303')
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Completed"
}
